casebody.data:
Arthur E. Burr, Frank L. Simpson and J. Howard Edwards as Trustees in Bankruptcy of the Port Tampa Phosphate Company, Appellants, v. Joseph Hull, Prairie Pebble Phosphate Company, a Corporation, and Savannah Trust Company, a Corporation, Appellees. An Appear from a Decree of the Circuit Court within and for the County of Polk. E. R. Gunby and James F. Glen, for Appellants. Geo. C. Bedell and Wilson & Swearingen, for Appellees.

Appeal dismissed on motion and stipulation of counsel for the respective parties.
